00:09:23.670 --> 00:09:25.330
But if you have
three dimensions,

00:09:25.330 --> 00:09:29.340
then we actually need,
at least apparently,

00:09:29.340 --> 00:09:32.790
we need three such quantities.

00:09:32.790 --> 00:09:37.010
So I need to put the
z subscript here.

00:09:37.010 --> 00:09:41.980
And then I need two more,
