kind of a straitjacket.

00:59:26.670 --> 00:59:30.480
Because it is
sinusoidally varying.

00:59:30.480 --> 00:59:34.110
But also, it must be
over such a period

00:59:34.110 --> 00:59:38.650
that it vanishes at the
edge of the waveguide.

